<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Cristiano Ronaldo - Portuguese Football Legend</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Professional CSS style for the title */
        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem; /* Adjust font size as needed */
            color: #333; /* Dark text color */
            text-align: center; /* Center align the text */
            margin-top: 80px; /* Add space below the title */
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; /* Use a clean sans-serif font */
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the title bold */
        }

        /* Style for footballer details */
        .footballer-details {
            margin: 30px auto; /* Center the footballer details */
            max-width: 600px; /* Limit width to improve readability */
            padding: 20px; /* Add padding for better visual appearance */
            background-color: #fff; /* White background color for footballer details */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Add shadow for depth */
        }

        /* Style for footballer image */
        .footballer-image {
            width: 100%; /* Ensure the image fills the container */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add rounded corners */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add space below the image */
        }

        /* Style for footballer name */
        .footballer-name {
            font-size: 1.8rem; /* Adjust font size for footballer name */
            color: #333; /* Dark text color */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Add space below the footballer name */
        }

        /* Style for footballer bio */
        .footballer-bio {
            font-size: 1.2rem; /* Adjust font size for footballer bio */
            color: #666; /* Dark gray text color */
            line-height: 1.5; /* Set line height for better readability */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add space below the footballer bio */
        }

        /* Apply linear gradient background */
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5, #e0e0e0); /* Light grey gradient colors */
            min-height: 100vh; /* Set minimum height to cover the viewport */
            display: flex; /* Use flexbox for vertical centering */
            flex-direction: column; /* Stack child elements vertically */
            justify-content: center; /* Center content horizontally */
            align-items: center; /* Center content vertically */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include header partial with navbar -->
    <% include partials/header %>

    <!-- Main content for Cristiano Ronaldo page -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="footballer-details">
            <img class="footballer-image" src="/images/image1.jpeg" alt="Cristiano Ronaldo">
            <h2 class="footballer-name">Cristiano Ronaldo</h2>
            <p class="footballer-bio">
                Cristiano Ronaldo is a Portuguese professional footballer widely regarded as one of the greatest players of all time. Born on February 5, 1985, in Funchal, Madeira, Portugal, Ronaldo has enjoyed an illustrious career spanning over two decades.
                <br><br>
                Ronaldo began his professional career with Sporting Lisbon before moving to Manchester United in 2003. During his time at Manchester United, Ronaldo won numerous titles, including three Premier League titles and the UEFA Champions League.
                <br><br>
                In 2009, Ronaldo made a record-breaking transfer to Real Madrid, where he further cemented his status as one of the best players in the world. He won four Champions League titles and became Real Madrid's all-time leading scorer before joining Juventus in 2018.
                <br><br>
                Known for his incredible athleticism, goal-scoring prowess, and unparalleled work ethic, Ronaldo has amassed numerous individual awards, including five FIFA Ballon d'Or titles. He is also the all-time leading scorer for the Portuguese national team.
                <br><br>
                Off the field, Ronaldo is known for his philanthropy and humanitarian efforts. He has donated millions of dollars to various charitable causes and continues to use his platform to advocate for positive social change.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include footer partial -->
    <% include partials/footer %>
</body>
</html>
